title: State Of Grace (Taylor's Version)
description:
What a beautiful song to kick off the Red era! What is this song about? Ana, Nick, Amy and Lacey go really deep into this song.. There is so much that it could all mean!
What did we miss? What would you like to hear from us? Lots of ways to reach us.. and we are really enjoying getting to hear from you all!
